# Rewilding and Oral Microbiome Study

This repository contains R scripts used for statistical analyses in:

"Neighborhood deadwood and yard rewilding modulate commensal microbiomes and inflammatory signals among urbanites"

## Requirements
- R version 4.3.1
- ANCOMBC
- lme4
- vegan
- phyloseq
- tidyverse
- rsq
- readr
- dplyr
- tibble

## R scripts
1. ANCOMBC_Rscript.R
2. LMM_models.R
